1. The completed and subsequently transferred projects to General Fund for proper recording;
2.CIP infrastructure assets amounting to 30.38 million;
3.CIP Buildings & Other Structures totalling P55million;
4.The full implementation and liquidation of the DSWD ECQ Special Ayuda amounting P212million;
